These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Game: billiard, go, mah-jongg, poker
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Game:billiard is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Game:go##2
4. Game:poker is on the far left##1
5. Game:mah-jongg is between Game:go and Game:billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | poker         | go   | mah-jongg | billiard       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Game: whist, poker, monopoly, chess
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Game:monopoly and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Game:chess is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Game:whist is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | poker | whist | monopoly | chess |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

