.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Food: cauliflower, corn, cranberry, kale
Color: white, ebony, light-blue, turquise
1. Color:light-blue is on the right of Food:kale##1
2. Color:light-blue is between Color:ebony and Food:corn##2
3. Color:ebony is on the far left##1
4. Color:turquise is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == Color:turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| Color   | ebony | light-blue   | turquise | white |

